/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 455, \"end\": 459, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9938747287148322e-20, \"text\": \"CGTN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\", \"Q141683\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The team's appearance at the Games will mark the fourth time for the Malkia Strikers to grace the Olympic stage.\", \"from\": 481, \"to\": 593, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 550, \"end\": 556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malkia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Malkia\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malkia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malkia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Kenya Women's volleyball team will be Africa's sole representatives in the sport in Paris.\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 689, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 599, \"end\": 604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.926170366692242, \"rank\": 0.07556021631138694, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 683, \"end\": 688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999086144313, \"rank\": 9.138548505036268e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The recently-crowned continental champions have been holding a training camp in Nairobi for the past three weeks.\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 803, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 770, \"end\": 777, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resourc