resource/Malkia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Malkia\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malkia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malkia\"}, {\"begin\": 1234, \"end\": 1239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999086144313, \"rank\": 9.138548505036268e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1279, \"end\": 1285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6753418360764127, \"rank\": 0.48052203467087734, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1287, \"end\": 1292, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.820840613927674, \"rank\": 0.21700842813572965, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1297, \"end\": 1303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8372619469421615, \"rank\": 0.1943681159497351, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After finishing 12th at Tokyo 2020, they have modest expectations of improving on their performance in France.\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1415, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1329, \"end\": 1334, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.981599682297432, \"rank\": 0.018745151730610164, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are in a tough pool, very tough pool, but we are preparing well to showcase our talent in Africa.\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1518, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We intend to improve and make more progress.\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1563, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But if we can win a match, that would be a plus to us,\\\" said Malkia Strikers head coach Japheth Munala.\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1667, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1625, \"end\": 1631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malkia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Malkia\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malkia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malkia\"}, {\"begin\": 1652, \"end\": 1659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japheth\", \"score\": 0.9999999999974989, \"rank\": 2.4885138360697293e-12, \"text\": \"Japheth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japheth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japheth\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 10-time African champions are relishing the opportunity to represent not only Kenya, but the entire continent in Paris.\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1792, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1751, \"end\": 1756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.926170366692242, \"rank\": 0.07556021631138694, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1786, \"end\": 1791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999908614431